<plot>Peace is declared in Northern Ireland after thirty years of troubles. The criminal empires that have existed during the troubles can no longer operate and are being shut down. Two petty criminals, overhear an English gang plotting to rob a money laundry, owned by the resident crime boss. Our heroes decide to beat the English gang to it and rob the factory themselves. This step is too far and they are forced to enlist the help of a gang from the other side of the community. Neither trusts each other, but the prize is worth the risk. The English gang becomes the least of their worries as the crime boss has a ruthless bodyguard, who has a keen interest in the security of the factory.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?543005</url></doc>
